title: Broncos party like it's 1999
text: Broncos party like it's 1999 David Polaski , dpolaski@muncie.gannett.com 11:50 p.m. EDT October 24, 2015 Buy Photo Daleville takes a team photo with the sectional trophy Saturday evening after winning the class 1A Cowan sectional final at Cowan High School. Daleville swept the sectional 3-0 in three neck and neck sets.
